Cell["\<\
Here is another quantum circuit model giving the same encoding. A possible \
advantage of this quantum circuit is that the CNOT gates are applied to \
nearest qubits (assuming that the qubits are physically arranged in the \
depicted order).\
\>", "TechNoteMathCaption",
 CellID->2043591497,ExpressionUUID->"13595835-d449-45cd-8208-be4b3f94b8cb"],

