 CellID->1499302334,ExpressionUUID->"6c417ee9-8015-4760-a85c-7b7472db6c06"],

Cell["\<\
The encoding process can be implemented either of the quantum circuits in \
Figure 3 or their equivalent variants. The first part of each quantum \
circuit, which is separated from the latter part by the vertical dotted line, \
is for the phase-flip encoding and the second part is to encode each block \
based on the bit-flip encoding.\
\>", "TechNoteText",
 CellID->321768901,ExpressionUUID->"883916f1-fc5e-42b2-9c4b-d34d5a394cc7"],

