  SuperscriptBox["6", "th"]], "InlineFormula",
  FontFamily->"Source Sans Pro",ExpressionUUID->
  "71ed03c0-297a-4a92-8ab7-03069f907204"],
 " qubit. However, one can apply the Pauli Z operator on any qubit of the \
second block to recover the original state."
}], "TechNoteMathCaption",
